- Of course.

1210
01:33:14,794 --> 01:33:18,329
- Now do you understand why we... ?
- Of course. Of course.

1211
01:33:18,464 --> 01:33:21,038
- Nothing's going to take it away from me.
- Nothing.

1212
01:33:21,175 --> 01:33:23,417
- Nobody must spoil it.
- Nobody.

1213
01:33:24,679 --> 01:33:27,135
- I've never...
- Of course.

1214
01:33:27,265 --> 01:33:29,304
- Never.
- Naturally.

1215
01:33:30,393 --> 01:33:32,433
Yes.

1216
