1320
01:41:40,542 --> 01:41:44,373
How about you sneaking away
with Katie Jones on a real fun picnic?

1321
01:41:44,503 --> 01:41:47,208
No telegrams,
no newspapers, no sermons.

1322
01:41:47,339 --> 01:41:50,340
The only business of the day will be us.
Just the two of us.

1323
01:41:50,467 --> 01:41:52,092
Oh, Shara.

