But...

1604
02:12:32,571 --> 02:12:34,813
this is their church.

1605
02:12:37,368 --> 02:12:39,325
Look!

1606
02:12:39,453 --> 02:12:41,659
Look! A shooting star!

1607
02:12:42,873 --> 02:12:44,533
It's a sign,

1608
02:12:44,667 --> 02:12:48,201
an omen for the glory that begins tonight.

1609
02:12:49,713 --> 02:12:51,587
Ready, Shara.

1610
02:12:51,715 --> 02:12:56,212
(choir)? Glory, glory, hallelujah

1611
02:12:56,428 --> 02:12:59,465
# Glory, glory, hallelujah

1612
02:12:59,598 --> 02:13:01,009
Wish me luck.

1613
02:13:01,141 --> 02:13:05,139
# Glory, glory, hallelujah

1614
02:13:05,271 --> 02:13:11,687
# His truth is marching on

1615
02:13:15,446 --> 02:13:18,447
If you believe in the faith
of your own Sister Sharon...

1616
02:13:18,575 --> 02:13:19,488
Yes!

1617
02:13:19,617 --> 02:13:22,239
. . if you believe in
the innocence of Elmer Gantry...

1618
02:13:22,370 --> 02:13:23,568
Yes!

1619
02:13:23,705 --> 02:13:27,239
- . . and if you believe in God Almighty...
- Yes!

1620
02:13:27,374 --> 02:13:30,660
. . reassure them with
a mighty "hallelujah"!

1621
02:13:30,794 --> 02:13:32,372
(loud cheering)

1622
02:13:51,356 --> 02:13:54,061
- Hallelujah, Sister!
- Hallelujah!

1623
02:14:12,502 --> 02:14:14,376
At this very moment,

1624
02:14:15,130 --> 02:14:19,424
the power of the Holy Ghost
has descended on this tabernacle.

1625
02:14:21,970 --> 02:14:24,010
He is here.

1626
02:14:24,932 --> 02:14:26,971
Here right now.

1627
02:14:27,267 --> 02:14:32,475
Just now, across the heavens,
towards the end of the world,

1628
02:14:32,981 --> 02:14:34,641
I saw an omen...

1629
02:14:35,150 --> 02:14:40,061
a fiery line written by the hand of God,
a glorious shooting star.

1630
02:14:41,031 --> 02:14:44,067
Thus, God has told us of his coming.

1631
02:14:44,785 --> 02:14:49,612
Have we lost God? Have we lost
contact with the supernatural?

1632
02:14:49,957 --> 02:14:54,250
Have we lost faith? Because
without faith, we are morally sick.

1633
02:14:54,586 --> 02:14:58,370
Faith... is the strongest force in the world.

1634
02:14:58,507 --> 02:15:00,630
Faith can raise the dead.

1635
02:15:00,759 --> 02:15:04,044
Faith can heal. Faith is the...

1636
02:15:04,178 --> 02:15:06,669
Help me, Sister! Help me!

1637
02:15:07,640 --> 02:15:09,679
Help me.

1638
02:15:10,768 --> 02:15:13,306
He can't hear, Sister. He's deaf.

1639
02:15:14,939 --> 02:15:17,512
Let him alone, please.

1640
02:15:28,953 --> 02:15:31,622
Help me, Sister.

1641
02:15:31,747 --> 02:15:34,155
Heal me.

1642
02:15:34,292 --> 02:15:36,368
(Morgan) You should take him to a doctor.

1643
02:15:36,502 --> 02:15:39,124
God is the greatest healer of all.

1644
02:15:39,839 --> 02:15:41,630
Was he born deaf?

1645
02:15:41,757 --> 02:15:45,458
A storm woke him up one night. He
screamed he couldn't hear the thunder.

1646
02:15:45,595 --> 02:15:48,595
- He could feel it but he couldn't hear it.
- You're his wife?

1647
02:15:48,723 --> 02:15:51,806
Yes, Sister. I'm sorry to trouble you.

1648
02:16:04,279 --> 02:16:08,193
Do you believe in the Father,
the Son, and the Holy Ghost?

1649
02:16:12,120 --> 02:16:16,414
Do you believe that Jesus
could heal by the laying on of hands,

1650
02:16:16,750 --> 02:16:20,700
and that he passed
this gift on to his disciples?

1651
02:16:22,005 --> 02:16:24,211
Pray with me, everyone.

1652
02:16:24,341 --> 02:16:27,674
Please pray with me. I need your faith.

1653
02:16:31,014 --> 02:16:33,386
O Lord...

1654
02:16:33,516 --> 02:16:36,553
O God, be merciful.

1655
02:16:41,190 --> 02:16:42,601
Heal.

1656
02:16:43,442 --> 02:16:44,640
Heal.

1657
02:16:50,533 --> 02:16:52,988
O God, help us in our weakness.

1658
02:16:53,911 --> 02:16:57,410
Punish us for our sins,
but reward us for our faith.

1659
02:17:01,293 --> 02:17:02,372
Heal.

1660
02:17:03,587 --> 02:17:05,212
Heal.

1661
02:17:08,884 --> 02:17:12,633
Let thy spirit fill this tabernacle.

1662
02:17:13,264 --> 02:17:16,549
Let thy holiness bless this house,

1663
02:17:16,934 --> 02:17:19,686
created for thy glory,

1664
02:17:19,812 --> 02:17:22,481
and thine alone.

1665
02:17:27,152 --> 02:17:28,528
Heal!

1666
02:17:28,654 --> 02:17:30,896
Pray for God to heal!

1667
02:17:31,031 --> 02:17:32,194
Heal!

1668
02:17:34,451 --> 02:17:36,491
God...

1669
02:17:43,878 --> 02:17:46,333
Can you hear me?

1670
02:17:49,091 --> 02:17:51,131
God, I...

1671
02:17:51,886 --> 02:17:54,886
I... I think I...

1672
02:17:57,683 --> 02:18:01,894
- Repeat after me. Blessed is the Lord.
- Blessed is the Lord.

1673
02:18:02,021 --> 02:18:06,433
- We thank thee, O Lord, for thy mercy.
- We thank thee, O Lord.

1674
02:18:07,401 --> 02:18:09,441
I can hear.

1675
02:18:10,404 --> 02:18:13,737
O God... I can hear!

1676
02:18:13,865 --> 02:18:17,364
Hallelujah! Hallelujah!

1677
02:18:17,493 --> 02:18:20,613
(choir sings "The Hallelujah Chorus")

1678
02:18:50,943 --> 02:18:53,019
Please wait. Please wait.

1679
02:18:53,946 --> 02:18:56,401
Don't... don't... don't get excited.

1680
02:18:58,075 --> 02:19:00,198
Oh, my God.

1681
02:19:03,163 --> 02:19:06,828
- Are you all right?
- Yes. Take care of the others, please.

1682
02:19:06,959 --> 02:19:09,414
You're in the house of God!

1683
02:19:25,852 --> 02:19:29,933
Those who believe in God will be saved.
Trust in the Lord!

1684
02:19:30,065 --> 02:19:32,223
Oh! Oh!

1685
02:20:07,810 --> 02:20:10,764
Are you all right, Shara? Shara? Shara?

1686
02:20:17,987 --> 02:20:20,858
- No. No. No. No. No!
- Shara!

1687
02:20:25,119 --> 02:20:26,744
Help!

1688
02:20:27,872 --> 02:20:29,070
No, please wait.

1689
02:20:31,584 --> 02:20:34,122
No, wait! Please, wait!

1690
02:20:44,764 --> 02:20:47,385
Wait! You must have faith!

1691
02:20:47,516 --> 02:20:49,556
- Wait!
- Shara!

1692
02:20:51,938 --> 02:20:52,969
Shara!

1693
02:20:55,608 --> 02:20:57,316
Shara!

1694
02:20:57,902 --> 02:20:59,313
Shara!

1695
02:21:00,655 --> 02:21:02,694
Shara! Shara!

1696
02:21:04,951 --> 02:21:06,231
Shara! Shara!

1697
02:23:05,527 --> 02:23:07,768
It's hers.

1698
02:23:10,198 --> 02:23:12,440
It's all we could find.

1699
02:24:00,539 --> 02:24:05,913
People everywhere would appreciate a
word from you, Mr. Gantry. Anything at all.

1700
02:24:07,629 --> 02:24:10,500
Speak to us, Mr. Gantry.

1701
02:24:12,926 --> 02:24:15,464
Please ask Sister Sharon to forgive us.

1702
