Hotter than the fires of damnation.

1704
02:24:21,435 --> 02:24:23,723
I ran. I was afraid.

1705
02:24:24,813 --> 02:24:27,600
Please ask Sister not to hate me.

1706
02:24:29,985 --> 02:24:32,274
Can you hear me up there, Sister?

1707
02:24:33,447 --> 02:24:35,688
Do you hate these folks?

1708
02:24:36,908 --> 02:24:39,944
She don't hate you. She loves you.

1709
02:24:40,077 --> 02:24:42,782
Praise the Lord and his love.

1710
